	<div class="block-content-header">
							<h6 class="b-content-section heading-square heading-border"><a href="/sections/sun-interview">The Sun Interview</a></h6>
		

				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/305/experiencing-deep-time">Experiencing Deep Time</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle">Brian Swimme On The Story Of The Universe</p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/renee-lertzman">Renee Lertzman</a></li><li><a href="/issues/305">May 2001</a></li></ul>

		

					</div>


